  "title": "斯坦福最火 CS 课：不让学生写代码，必须用 AI",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651006067&idx=2&sn=7d293c529bab755cc10733110ecde322",
  "date": "2025-12-08 10:09:00",
